    <p class="title title-1">Welcome to Edmonton City Centre’s #31DaysOfHappy</p>
    </div>
  </header>


  <div class="first-element">
    <img class="image" src="//kodekloud.s3.amazonaws.com/sites/554273926e6f644145000000/113ac792b12dc4294a837af09c8ee82e/ECC_31_DAYS_HAPPYFACE_fnl(2).png">
    <p>
      When asked what someone wants most out of life, the majority would answer: ‘I just want to be happy.’ Yet many of us lead lives that are too rushed, too stressed and too focused on things that don’t really matter. For some of us, our lifestyles are making us physically and mentally unwell – they’re making us unhappier, not happier. For the month of May, Edmonton City Centre is sprinkling a little happiness to its retailers, shoppers and the downtown community.
    </p>
  </div>
  <br>

<div class="container clearfix">
    <div class="element element-2"></div>
    <p class="text text-2"><strong>31 Acts of Happiness : </strong>
    City Centre will facilitate 31 surprise acts of happiness - one for each day of May! 31 of our fabulous retailers will be sponsoring a day in May and our Guest Services team will choose a person daily, at random, to give an awesome gift to. The only way to win is by visiting Edmonton City Centre! Also, be sure to visit our Guest Services booth (located on the Street Level) for a happy-face button that you can wear all month long to show your commitment to #31DaysofHappy.</p>
    <div class="element element-3"></div>
 
    <br>
        <strong style="margin-top:30px">Happiness in 31 Deeds Challenge :</strong> 
        Imagine a world where everybody makes a commitment to do deeds that bring happiness to a loved one, friend or a complete stranger and doesn’t ask for something in return. Wouldn’t that be awesome!? YOU can make that happen! Join Edmonton City Centre’s <strong>Happiness in 31 Deeds Challenge</strong> and spread the happiness! Become a fan of our Facebook page  <a href="//www.facebook.com/ShopEdmontonCityCentre">here</a>)
        Each day we will post a simple happiness challenge on our page for you to complete. All you have to do is take photographic evidence that you’ve completed the challenge that day and post it on Facebook, Twitter or Instagram. Don’t forget to tag us <strong>@EdmontonCityCentre</strong> on Facebook or <strong>@ECCMALL</strong> on Twitter and Instagram and use the hashtag #31DaysOfHappy. If you complete all 31 challenges you’ll be eligible to win these fantastic prizes:
      </p> <br>
      <p><strong>“Escape to a Happy Place”</strong> – 31 movie tickets to Landmark Cinemas</p>
      <p><strong>“Happy Camper”</strong> – 31 ways to play in Jasper - two night getaway at Jasper Park Lodge</p>
      <p><strong>“Money Can Buy Happiness”</strong> - $3,100 in Edmonton City Centre gift cards</p>
    <br>      
